<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg von Seckendorff, Hauptmann zu Cadolzburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung des zu Cadolzburg gefangenen Heinz Quetrer, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_206" id="102r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_206_r1l13"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Gorgen von Seckendorff Hawbtman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l14">cʒü Cadolcʒburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_206_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Gorg vns iſt furbracht worden wie das Jr vnſern bürger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l16">heincʒen Qwetrer cʒü Cadolcʒburg gefangen habt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l17"><expan>egenan<ex>ten</ex></expan> vnſern̈ burger durch vnſern̈ willen ledig wöllet laſſen Als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l18">etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_206" id="102r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Gorgen von Seckendorff, hawbtman czü
                        Cadolczburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Gorg, uns ist
                                                furbracht worden, wie das ir unsern bürger Heinczen
                                                Qwetrer czü Cadolczburg gefangen habt.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                                  <expan>egenan<ex>ten</ex></expan> unsern burger
                                                durch unsern willen ledig wöllet lassen. Als etc.
                                                Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
